data.description: Welcome to your ideal family haven! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence has both comfort and style. As you approach this delightful property, you'll be struck by its curb appeal, featuring well-manicured landscaping and a welcoming entrance. Step inside, and you'll notice fresh paint in all the common areas, adding light to the home. With an open-concept living and dining area, it creates an inviting space for gatherings with friends and family. A spacious bar and breakfast area offers a relaxed atmosphere for enjoying your morning coffee or hosting casual meals. One of the standout features of this property is the converted garage, now a versatile TV/playroom. This space offers endless possibilities, whether you envision cozy movie nights, energetic playtime for the kids, or a tranquil retreat to unwind with your favorite shows. The three bedrooms in this home offer comfortable retreats, each uniquely designed to cater to your family's needs. The primary bedroom boasts an en-suite bathroom, ensuring privacy and convenience. The additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed and share a well-maintained bathroom.Stepping outside, you'll discover a spacious backyard that beckons you to enjoy the great outdoors. This ample outdoor space invites you to create your own oasis, whether it's setting up a barbecue area for weekend cookouts, tending to your garden, or providing a playground for the kids. It's a canvas for your imagination. Don't miss the chance to make this house your forever home - schedule a viewing today!
